      <item>
        <title>CentOS快速配置多台机器为静态地址</title>
        <link>http://junjie2018.github.io/notes/%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/centos/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8/centos%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%B0%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%BA%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://junjie2018.github.io/notes/%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/centos/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8/centos%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%B0%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%BA%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80/</guid>
        <description>指令如下，这是我目前找到的最优雅，最快速的方法： nmcli connection modify eth0 \ ipv4.dns 192.168.31.199 \ ipv4.method manual \ ipv4.gateway 192.168.31.199 \ connection.autoconnect yes nmcli c up eth0 nmcli connection modify eth0 \ ipv4.addresses 192.168.23.60/24 \ ipv4.dns 192.168.23.65 \ ipv4.method manual \ ipv4.gateway 192.168.23.65 \ connection.autoconnect yes nmcli c up eth0 # 访问</description>
      </item>
      
